 {{in lang|de}}</ref>\n\n==Honours==\n;KF La\u00e7i\n* [[Albanian Cup]] (1): 2014\u201315\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Selala, Anthimos}}\n[[Category:1994 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from La\u00e7]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Albanian footballers]]\n[[Category:KF La\u00e7i players]]\n[[Category:Albanian Superliga players]]\n[[Category:Albanian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Albanian expatriate sportspeople in Greece]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Greece]]\n[[Category:Albanian expatriate sportspeople in Germany]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Germany]]\n\n\n{{Albania-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Orphan|date=July 2018}}\n\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Anthimos Selala\n| image = \n| fullname = Anthimos Selala\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1994|2|9}}\n| birth_place = [[La\u00e7]], [[Albania]]\n| position = [[Midfielder]]\n| currentclub = \n| clubnumber = \n| youthyears1 =  2012\u20132013\n| youthclubs1 = [[KF La\u00e7i|La\u00e7i]]\n| years1 =  2013\u20132014<ref>[http://www.inewsgr.com/158/asteras-varis-apektise-ton-nearo-selala.htm \u0391\u03c3\u03c4\u03ad\u03c1\u03b1\u03c2 \u0392\u03ac\u03c1\u03b7\u03c2: \u0391\u03c0\u03ad\u03ba\u03c4\u03b7\u03c3\u03b5 \u03c4\u03bf\u03bd \u03bd\u03b5\u03b1\u03c1\u03cc \u03a3\u03b5\u03bb\u03ac\u03bb\u03b1]</ref>\n| clubs1 =  [[Kyanos Asteras Vari F.C.|Kyanos Asteras Vari]]\n| caps1 =   \n| goals1 =  \n| years2 =  2014\n| clubs2 =  [[KF La\u00e7i|La\u00e7i]]\n| caps2 =   1\n| goals2 =  0\n| years3 =  2015\n| clubs3 =  [[P.O Dafni Dafnona]]\n| caps3 =   11\n| goals3 =  4\n| years4 =  2016\n| clubs4 =  [[A.P.O Kanaris Neniton]]\n| caps4 =   \n| goals4 =  \n| years5 = 2017\n| clubs5 = [[TuSpo Weser-Gimte]]\n| caps5 =   \n| goals5 =\n\n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1 =  \n| nationalcaps1 =    \n| nationalgoals1 =   \n| pcupdate = \n| ntupdate = \n}}\n'''Anthimos Selala''' (born 9 February 1994 in [[La\u00